description:
The frogs invite the Hinata siblings to go golfing.  Everything seems fine at first -- but something`s strange about the golf course.  And why do they keep hearing 556 laughing?  After that, they get an exercise machine that`s booby-trapped from Viper, and Keroro has to figure out WHICH Viper in order to save his friends!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Keroro, Keron-Style Golf / Keroro, Run Keroro
ケロロ ケロン式ゴルフ / ケロロ 走れケロロ
